                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Punch Petrol ARAI:</span>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Manual: ~18.8 kmpl</li>
                            <li>AMT: ~18.8 kmpl</li>
                            <li>CNG: ~27.0 km/kg</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <p><span class="font-weight-700">Takeaway:</span> Swift outperforms Punch significantly in fuel economy. The mild-hybrid variant extends this lead further. CNG trims also favor Swift for mileage.</p>

