                </ul>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">Driving Experience</h2>

                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Swift</span> — Sporty, light-handling feel typical of hatchbacks. SHVS mild-hybrid adds low-end torque/nimbleness.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Punch</span> — Positioned more softly, ride tuned for comfort. Lower torque peak favors relaxed driving.</li>
                </ul>

