                    <li>If <span class="font-weight-700">efficiency</span>, <span class="font-weight-700">compactness</span>, and <span class="font-weight-700">driver engagement</span> top your list, go for the <span class="font-weight-700">Swift</span>, especially the mild-hybrid or CNG version.</li>
